# Note durations

Note durations are defined using:

* duration characters (a-z)
  * dotted & tied notes
* decimals
  * random durations
  
**Common durations:**

|	Character	|	Note length	|	Note name (US)	|	Note name (UK)	|
| - | --- | ------- | ----- |
|	w	|	1.0	|	Whole note	|	Semibreve	|
|	h	|	0.5	|	Half noteÂ 	|	Minim	|
|	q	|	0.25	|	Quarter note	|	Crotchet	|
|	e	|	0.125	|	8th note	|	Quaver	|
|	s	|	0.0625	|	16th note	|	Semiquaver	|

